node.title: Milk tanker crash closes SH1 off-ramp in Waikato
node.description: A milk tanker rolled on the off-ramp of State Highway 1 near Taupiri, blocking the road.
node.content:
["A milk tanker has rolled on an off-ramp of State Highway 1 near Taupiri, blocking the road.", "", "
\nPhoto: 123RF\n
", "Police said the tanker rolled about 2.30am on the southbound off-ramp.", "No injuries have been reported.", "Emergency services were the scene and the road was closed while the tanker was being moved.", "Motorists were asked avoid the area or follow diversion signs."]
